source.name: FAFSA Application Volume
source.description: These reports provide information on the number of Free Applications for Federal Student Aid (FAFSAs) processed.  One report provides the number of applications by the applicant's state of legal residence and the other report provides the number of applications by postsecondary institution, as listed on the applicant's FAFSA.  In both reports, numbers are reported in two categories: dependent students and independent students.
